{
  "stem": "1603.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I was always concerned about other people in my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I got up, and I walked to them real far away, and I asked their permission, can I sit down?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they said yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I told them what happened to me last night, that we got arrested, we got shot at with machine guns on the border-- I didn't tell you that-- when they stopped us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so I'm telling this story to these people to talk them out of this escape effort.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because I said, you can't leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So this boy says, what are you telling me?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He said, I just came back from Austria, and this is my girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I went back to Budapest, and we are here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And tomorrow morning, we're going to Austria again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I said-- I was shocked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I said, that's the kind of connections you have?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He says, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I said, could we join you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And because he saw how much I was concerned about his life, he let me go with him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he had sensational contacts at the border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that's how for the second time we made it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And that's how I-- I got to Austria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then when I got to Austria, I went to the Free Europe station, radio station, and gave a coded signal to my sister and mother that I'm here and come.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my sister came, but my mother was too cowardly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother always felt that we're never going to make anything, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I just couldn't live with that anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she could have made it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they couldn't give up things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I gave everything up in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I still was semi-wealthy.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
